          },
          "reviewBody": "On Jessore Road, there are multiple \"Aditya\" institutes. The colorful one, bit inside, behind IDENTITY apartment is the Senior Secondary School. Whereas the one right on Jessore Road & opposite Diamond Plaza is the \"Secondary School\" (this used to be the \"Aditya Nursing Home \").\nIn between these two, you have Aditya Sports Academy as well (adjacent to Shyamnagar Crossing).\n\nCan't really comment on how these schools are. But went there during SOF - Science Olympiad Foundation exams and the organizer's were quite lousy. This may or may not be direct responsibility of the school, but one can't wash off their hands.",
